953
00:36:02,020 --> 00:36:05,420
is that the divergence of the velocity field

954
00:36:05,420 --> 00:36:06,340
is equal to zero.

955
00:36:06,480 --> 00:36:08,320
Let's drop this factor here,

956
00:36:08,460 --> 00:36:09,760
it doesn't do anything for us.

957
00:36:11,080 --> 00:36:14,180
dvx by dx plus dvy by dy

958
00:36:14,180 --> 00:36:15,720
is equal to zero.

959
00:36:16,790 --> 00:36:18,540
This is not a general rule

960
00:36:18,540 --> 00:36:20,280
about all possible flows.

961
00:36:20,720 --> 00:36:22,840
This is a rule about

962
00:36:22,840 --> 00:36:24,440
incompressible flows

963
00:36:25,890 --> 00:36:27,740
that start with uniform density

964
00:36:27,740 --> 00:36:30,500
and maintain the uniformity of the density.

965
00:36:31,120 --> 00:36:32,720
Notice that it does not say

966
00:36:32,720 --> 00:36:34,380
