00:37:46,560 --> 00:37:47,480
it's not going out there.

1008
00:37:48,540 --> 00:37:48,980
Okay.

1009
00:37:50,420 --> 00:37:52,380
So that argument applies to any space?

1010
00:37:52,760 --> 00:37:54,780
It applies to any number of dimensions.

