00:38:04,080 --> 00:38:04,920
x,

1016
00:38:04,920 --> 00:38:05,920
y,

1017
00:38:05,920 --> 00:38:08,280
and z here just refer to a general space

1018
00:38:08,280 --> 00:38:09,880
having nothing to do with mechanics,

1019
00:38:10,140 --> 00:38:12,600
just a general flow in any number of dimensions.

